uw koelkast kapot is?


423
00:44:20.625 --> 00:44:21.793
Nee, ik heb niet gebeld.

424
00:44:23.336 --> 00:44:25.839
Dit is Unit 301, nummer 18, toch?

425
00:44:26.673 --> 00:44:29.467
Dit is nummer 16.
Nummer 18 is daar.


426
00:44:30.510 --> 00:44:31.719
Sorry, verkeerde plek dus.

427
00:44:40.728 --> 00:44:41.813
Falun Gong!

